Introduction

Rona is a Taiwanese singer under FC ENM. She used to be a trainee of TPE48 (now AKB48 Team TP) and a participant in the survival show Girls Planet 999. She made her official debut on April 4, 2022, as a member of the girl group ILY:1.

On July 7, 2021, she was confirmed as an upcoming contestant on Mnet's newest reality show, Girls Planet 999. In the fifth episode, which was aired on September 3, it was revealed that Rona, along with her cellmates, was unfortunately eliminated.
